div.div:
Extract the URI of the movie that is currently viewed.
Extract a list of all the actors starring in the movie.
Extract a list of the genres the movie is classified under.
Extract a list of the directors that contributed in the making of the film.
All these can be found in the current view. All the elements of the lists will
be separated by "|separator|" to avoid conflicts with other symbols.
All the extracted data is url encoded and sent as query string to the
recommendations service

div.div:
Process the recommendation results for each of
the parameters. The final form will be a dictionary
containing a key for 'actors', one for 'directors' and
one for 'genres'. On each of these keys there will be
another dictionary as value. This dictionary will contain
on its keys the URI's of the movies found, and on its
values a list of all the titles that movie is known by.
